_sText:
Fun_underwater_bunker beta - a fun, bomb defuse map where bombsite is underwater :)

There are 4 driveable vechicles.

Buyzone is on the first island next to respawn of a team.

Terrorists must detonate aztec buildings, CT's must prevent them.

ITS FUN MAP, BECAUSE THERE ARE MANY VECHICLES, UNDERWATER BOMBSITE, FUNNY GAMEPLAY :)

Thanks for playing :)
